{
  "api": "PayFit Partner API (https://partner-api.payfit.com) plus legacy customer /v1 endpoints retained for migration parity",
  "docs": "https://developers.payfit.io/llms.txt (merged official per-endpoint OpenAPI blocks from /reference/*.md)",
  "reviewed_at": "2026-07-04",
  "scope": "Pass B expansion: preserves the 3 legacy /v1 read streams and covers PayFit's current reference surface from llms.txt. JSON list/detail endpoints become streams, JSON customer-key mutations become writes, binary/PDF/CSV/multipart and partner/auth helper endpoints are explicitly excluded with closed categories.",
